snippet.title: House 2 - Official Teaser | Tokyo Game Show 2023
snippet.description:
WARNING: GRAPHIC CONTENT. House 2 is the sequel by Bark Bark Games to their hit 2020 indie horror game. Wishlist it on Steam now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2586440/House_2/?beta=0

House 1 is coming to consoles soon! Buy it now on Steam! 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1444350/House/
